General.Name: mwb fairtrade Wertpapierhandelsbank AG
General.Description: mwb fairtrade Wertpapierhandelsbank AG operates as a securities trading company in Germany. It provides order books for German and international securities, including equities, fixed income securities, and mutual funds. The company also offers capital market services, which includes issuance advice and listing, designated sponsorships, debt and equity capital markets, tokenized capital market, institutional customer care, and order execution services. mwb fairtrade Wertpapierhandelsbank AG was founded in 1993 and is headquartered in Gräfelfing, Germany.
